<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center">
  <header class="text-center mb-8 w-full">
    <h1 class="p-20 text-5xl font-bold bg-blue-200">
      NW利用制限一括確認
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-8">
      エラーになったら手動で各リンクから確認してください<br>
      docomo/au/softbankのみ一括判定なので<br>
      楽天/mineoは下記リンクから手動でお願いします。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <a
        href="http://nw-restriction.nttdocomo.co.jp/search.php"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-300 transition"
      >【docomo】</a>

      <a
        href="https://my.au.com/cmn/WCV009001/WCE009001.hc?_gl=1*1k8zk6o*_ga*MTA2NzUwNTQwOC4xNzQ5NDAzNDQz*_ga_LQGLLT5T9S*czE3NjY1NDU3MTYkbzIkZzEkdDE3NjY1NDU3MjIkajU0JGwwJGgw*_ga_NEDL1XGXY7*czE3NjY1NDU3MTYkbzIyJGcxJHQxNzY2NTQ1NzIyJGo1NCRsMCRoMA.."
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 transition"
      >【AU】</a>

      <a
        href="https://ct99.my.softbank.jp/WBF/icv?_gl=1*1fo5ue1*_gcl_au*MTEyOTM5MjY2MS4xNzY2NTQ1OTE3"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition"
      >【SoftBank】</a>

      <a
        href="https://network.mobile.rakuten.co.jp/restriction/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-pink-600 hover:text-pink-300 transition"
      >【Rakuten】</a>

      <a
        href="https://my.mineo.jp/info/GNS010101GNS010101_Init.action"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-300 transition"
      >【mineo】</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-grow flex justify-center w-full pb-24">
    <form
      class="flex flex-col w-full max-w-md"
      action="/check"
      method="post"
    >
      <input
        type="hidden"
        name="authenticity_token"
        value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>"
      >

      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
        IMEI番号
      </label>

      <p
        id="error"
        class="text-sm text-red-500 mt-2 hidden"
      >
        IMEIは15桁の数字で入力してください
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <input
          type="text"
          id="imei"
          name="imei"
          placeholder="15桁のIMEIを入力"
          maxlength="15"
          inputmode="numeric"
          autocomplete="on"
          class="flex-1 rounded-lg border px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-blue-300"
        >

        <button
          type="button"
          id="clearBtn"
          class="px-3 rounded-lg border text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
        >
          クリア
        </button>

        <button
          type="button"
          id="copyBtn"
          class="px-3 rounded-lg border text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
        >
          コピー
        </button>
      </div>

      <button
        type="submit"
        id="submitBtn"
        disabled
        class="w-full mt-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-white bg-gray-400 transition-colors duration-300 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
      >
        判定する
      </button>

      <div
        id="result"
        class="hidden text-lg mt-8 w-full max-w-md text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">判定結果</h2>

        <ul class="text-center space-y-2">
          <li>docomo：<span id="docomo">－</span></li>
          <li>au：<span id="au">－</span></li>
          <li>SoftBank：<span id="softbank">－</span></li>
          <%# <li>Rakuten：<span id="rakuten">－</span></li> %>
          <%# <li>mineo：<span id="mineo">－</span></li> %>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div
        id="loading"
        class="hidden mt-4 flex justify-center"
      >
        <div
          class="h-6 w-6 animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-blue-300 border-t-blue-600"
        ></div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </main>

  <div
    id="toast"
    class="fixed top-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gray-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-lg opacity-0 pointer-events-none transition-opacity duration-300"
  >
    コピーしました！
  </div>

  <footer class="mt-auto pt-7 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
    <small>&copy; 2025 jojo</small>
  </footer>
</body>
